    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219180/extras/b0bca3150bfe6d6ce3c83248ab930c6e.avif?t=1757673570\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个充满耐心的人，用自己的的双手去调整他所见到的这个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《平衡97.261/100》是一款使用双手精准摆放物品的游戏，有点难，但是只要冷静与耐心，即可到达终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219180/extras/c558e127f7f6e35bdf5bf6dd45875442.poster.avif?t=1757673570\" width=616 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219180/extras/c558e127f7f6e35bdf5bf6dd45875442.webm?t=1757673570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219180/extras/c558e127f7f6e35bdf5bf6dd45875442.mp4?t=1757673570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把地砖旋转至正确角度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把凌乱的书籍垂直堆好。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把美术馆里的画作摆正。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把洗手液盖子转动成一个方向。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至能让地球回到她应该在的位置。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏也支持多人模式，一人控制一个手，希望你与你的伙伴能达到同步率100%。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219180/extras/b0bca3150bfe6d6ce3c83248ab930c6e.avif?t=1757673570\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于开发者 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是<strong>Liujiajun</strong>，这是我第<strong>六</strong>部上Steam的游戏，希望你能喜欢我的作品，感谢你的游玩。</p>",
